/SCN/XXOTE/XX. Biblical references include Isaiah 52:2, 51:17, 60:1; Judges 5:12;
Isaiah 60:1, 54:4; Psalm 42:12; Isaiah 14:32, Jeremiah 30:18, 16; Isaiah
49:19, 62:5, 54:3, and 25:9./PR
